The paper deals with a machine learning problem of Partial Label Learning (PLL) and proposes a novel Graph Matching based approach to solve it. The paper involves techniques from graph theory, probabilistic matching, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
